\begin_layout Section
OH calls any hand
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
Reason: Tablemap does not detect bet amounts.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
If OpenHoldem calls every hand --- except maybe the strong ones --- this
 is probably neither a bug in OpenHoldem nor bad logic in the bot but a
 problem with the Tablemap or with your settings again: It most probably
 does not recognize your opponents bet, so OpenHoldem thinks, you have a
 free check and calls.
